title: DC-12
description:
It's RARE that I upload however I hope I will change.

This is a somewhat low quality 128 kbps MP3 that I ironically find tolerable!

This was on the Defcon 13 official CD that everyone received or the first however many to register as I was in the first 100 to register, I don't know if it was the first 100 or 1000 or 8192 (I did get a badge, too)

So, this was some of the music picked by Defcon 12 to be included.  I just wish it was at least 256 kbps.  The speaker farts are irritating sometimes because of the 128...

Hey, one advantage to the 128 is that you should be able to seed it to at least 1:1 on your end.  Please???

COMMENT!
